OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRio Tinto says 21 female   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fworkers reported sexual    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fassaults                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Anglo-Australian miner Rio Tinto says  
OL,6, 21 of its female employees reported an 
OL,7, actual or attempted rape or sexual     
OL,8, assault at work in the past five years.
OL,10,FThe mining giant - which operates in 35
OL,11,Fcountries - did not provide details on 
OL,12,Fthe incidents or where they took place.
OL,14,FBut the numbers were revealed in a     
OL,15,Fwider workplace culture report that    
OL,16,Ffound sexism, racism and bullying      
OL,17,Fsystemic across the firm.              
OL,19,FIt follows recent scrutiny over the    
OL,20,Ftreatment of women at mining camps.    
